Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了要拯救世界的所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.93,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离走向毁灭的大崩落危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.64,0:00:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不断旅行的里德，法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.14,0:00:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.64,0:00:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.97,0:00:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停留的海上都市·贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了许多的迷团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.88,0:00:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在地下的“奈雷特福音”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.28,0:00:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有等待里德他们的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又将会如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.89,0:00:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…故事已渐入佳境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.79,0:02:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9话  被夺走的大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种景象我还是头一次看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.31,0:02:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个普拉提亚小姐  蜜妮玛小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这景象每年都会发生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.98,0:02:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的  没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.42,0:02:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，你们两个不是都说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.99,0:02:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话要跟我说吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下再慢慢跟你说好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.30,0:02:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他那样的笑脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然让人觉得好感动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.94,0:02:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要去找里德吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.99,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.49,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔，书很有趣吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.21,0:03:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，在这本书里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然记载了历史上所有的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却都是至今从未听说的奇异事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.85,0:03:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去我所研读过的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记载的都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以创造神赛法特为主的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这本书里面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.76,0:03:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描述的却都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以破坏神奈雷特为主的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是头一次看到这样的书呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且不谈那些怪兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真的是疑云重重呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.58,0:03:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时候…到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必今晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会是个令人难忘的夜晚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到对面的山崖看的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色会更美哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.77,0:04:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要观赏景色的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是绝对值得推荐的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你们带我去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.31,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很乐意替你带路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了这座桥马上就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~这座桥还真不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.96,0:04:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不呢  它已经很老旧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.40,0:04:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，跟台风那天走的吊桥比起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要安心多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座桥不晓得哪一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会掉下来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂   拜托饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛  蜜妮玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.98,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这种话未免太不吉利了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险好险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉提亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.75,0:05:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在打水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子因为台风的灾害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本在旅馆工作的员工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.86,0:05:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部回去重建家园了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这场雨暂时不会停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.09,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我今天从早上就一直在工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.59,0:06:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只要一想到里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.32,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变成这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许因为我们是青梅竹马的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直都在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.97,0:07:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候会觉得好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有血缘关系的兄弟姐妹一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法把他当作一个男人看待…吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能那么干脆承认的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就简单多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也被里德所吸引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很有本领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑术又高超
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我被他吸引的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.99,0:07:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里特很喜欢望着天空看不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.80,0:07:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要跟那家伙在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.13,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会有一种望着晴空的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.24,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么忧虑或是烦恼都能全部忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人内心感到非常安详
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心，我没有想要对他怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.69,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天之所以会讲这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是海上祭典之夜的关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你看那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.07,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德  里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听到啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  那是真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的，这里有写啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的确是能解释所有的疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…假如这上面写的是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们留在贝鲁卡纽会有危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾神奈雷特啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此献上里德·哈谢尔的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里喊是听不到的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.64,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点通知大家才行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.63,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.25,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉提亚小姐…对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是蜜妮玛对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.18,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.12,0:10:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁沙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.16,0:10:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个…为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧，里特？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是什么大不了的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.77,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要阻止我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法跟这两个人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能跟她们打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.01,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.05,0:11:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是在开玩笑，对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.02,0:11:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想半开玩笑的吓吓我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不小心   玩笑开过头了对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，或许从一开始我们就输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们动手杀里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是下不了手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么要杀里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来替她们解释吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是赛雷斯提亚人的后裔吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我看书的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.64,0:12:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现一个很奇怪的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是距离现在2000年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚和赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在战争的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说有一部份的赛雷斯提亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在茵费利亚大陆上登陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这传说是真的的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.28,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候存活的赛雷斯提亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样隐藏身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直留在茵费利亚上面生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话所有迷题就能解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.06,0:13:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些岛上的遗迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有怪兽身上有艾拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都可以做解释了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们贝鲁卡岛的岛民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过2000年的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直隐瞒着赛雷斯提亚的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地生活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.91,0:13:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了履行祖先遗留下来的大目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是大目的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.42,0:13:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.94,0:13:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁卡纽的领主艾克丝提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的另一个身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.02,0:14:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的身分就是颠覆茵费利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚的祭司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“奈雷特福音”的总帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“奈雷特福音”？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.63,0:14:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的祖先就是来到这个土地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与茵费利亚军勇敢战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚的圣战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.70,0:14:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…悲剧产生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这陆地的我们的祖先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当战争一直激烈的进行着的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.05,0:14:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然  世界有了大变动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队无法回到赛雷斯提亚去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在基地里面的祖先们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.83,0:14:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这个外交极少的这座岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏赛雷斯提亚人的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地在这里过生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.74,0:14:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对茵费利亚的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样代代延续下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那也是到现在为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.18,0:15:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请快点逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领的真正目的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收声！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.99,0:15:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要那种没有用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可以这样做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.78,0:15:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.28,0:15:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎牙破斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚   卧龙空破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂，用大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.09,0:16:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾水之医治来保护汝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊弗力特  西尔夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.06,0:16:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾之炙热魔掌熔化为灰烬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空之风啊  降下来并化为龙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没舒展筋骨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.85,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.75,0:16:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕裂  风刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.76,0:17:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.17,0:17:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在等这个时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.78,0:17:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜，现在就让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶灵起了反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.01,0:17:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实体快支持不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.14,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…她制御着大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个女孩与生俱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.54,0:18:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召引晶灵的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.07,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.17,0:18:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那时候是因为可莉娜的出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股强大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用在赛雷斯提亚的技术上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连大晶灵也一样会受控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.19,0:18:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务已经完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没有利用价值了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你们看看我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚的技术吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.24,0:18:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…大晶灵的招数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.54,0:18:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔神剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.61,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.48,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大晶灵的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.49,0:19:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是到我的手中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样几千年的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于可以如愿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…如果没有大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.18,0:19:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要这些大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.79,0:19:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大晶灵还给我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出现在里德他们的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.73,0:19:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们就是里德身边的一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲切的岛民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是经过2000年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着代代继承的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报复即将开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待下场好戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（次回预告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.99,0:21:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人怀念的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.03,0:21:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到生命结束的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回   消失在夕阳里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.73,0:21:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个“塔斯帖克”到底是谁？


